strings: <voice_0x01000EE9><se_def>The prince Carlos: Is it Arjuna's soul? But he is still very young!
<voice_0x01000EEA><se_def>The prince Carlos: The occult gecko didn't seem concerned.
<voice_0x01000EEB><se_def>The prince Carlos: We have to hunt chameleons until there are enough chameleons to respect their behavior.
<voice_0x01000EEC><se_high>Accuracy: What will happen to those who escape with the least risk? Don't mock me...
<voice_0x01000EED><se_low>January: He meets again<:> "He's not old", "Here's a knife", "He still thinks he has a chance!"
<voice_0x01000EEE><se_def>China: According to legend, he forgot who he was to fight in battle royale...
